#==========================================================
# EVENT BOOKING FLOW
#==========================================================

### 1. Calculate Event Booking (Preview — no transaction created)
# Use this to show the user a price breakdown before they commit.
# - For Single Ticket type: pass "ticketId" and "qty".
# - For Multi-Ticket selections: pass "tickets" array instead.
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/calculate
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "tickets": [
        {
            "ticketId": "6a2904739f3feca6e22f4f99",
            "qty": 2
        }
    ],
    "discountCode": "",
    "bookingType": "EVENT",
    "eventId": "6a2904739f3feca6e22f4f98"
}

### 2. Calculate Event Booking WITH Promo Code
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/calculate
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "ticketId": "{{ticketId}}",
  "qty": 1,
  "discountCode": "SUMMER2026"
}

### 3. Initiate Event Booking (Creates PENDING transaction)
# - For Single Ticket type: pass "ticketId" and "qty".
# - For Multi-Ticket selections: pass "tickets" array instead.
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/initiate
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "discountCode": "",
 "tickets": [
   { "ticketId": "{{ticketId}}", "qty": 2 }
  ]
}

### 4. Confirm Payment (Mock — transitions PENDING → PAID)
# Use the transactionId returned from the initiate step
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/confirm-payment
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "{{transactionId}}"
}

### 5. Get My Event Tickets (Upcoming) — Paginated
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/list?bookingType=COURSE&type=upcoming&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 6. Get My Event Tickets (Past) — Paginated
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/list?bookingType=EVENT&type=past&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 7. Get All My Event Tickets — Paginated
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/list?bookingType=EVENT&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 8. Get Ticket Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/detail/6a4ccaa2084c571553c54b4f
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiI2YTM4ZTA3MDU4ZWQxNGQ1YTZmNjFmZjEiLCJyb2xlSWQiOjIsImlhdCI6MTc4MzA4NTc2NSwiZXhwIjoyNjQ3MDg1NzY1fQ.7P9TcWn_4fYJ1DhrSUTfVTNAbfWa7dVpAnE0dFRgeno

### 9. Generate Share & Download URLs
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/public/generate-urls/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 10. Get Public Ticket Detail (No auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/public/detail/{{transactionId}}

### 10b. Download Public Ticket PDF (No auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/public/ticket/download/{{transactionId}}

#==========================================================
# EVENT ATTENDEE MANAGEMENT (Organizer)
#==========================================================

### 11. Get Event Attendees List
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/event/{{eventId}}/attendees
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 11b. Get Event Attendees List — Paginated, Search by Name or bookingId (single field)
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/event/{{eventId}}/attendees?page=1&limit=5&search=New
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 12. Get Event Attendees — Checked-in Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/event/{{eventId}}/attendees?status=checked-in
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 13. Get Event Attendees — Not Checked-in
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/event/{{eventId}}/attendees?status=not-checked-in
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 14. Get Event Attendee Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/event/{{eventId}}/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 14b. Get Unique Event Attendees List (With Aggregated Ticket details, transaction details & pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/event/attendees/{{eventId}}?page=1&limit=5&search=
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}



### 15. Scan QR Code (Gate Keeper Check-in)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/scan-qr
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "qrCodeData": "TICKET-REPLACE_TXN_ID-REPLACE_USER_ID-1234567890"
}

### 15b. Refund Preview (Check policy & refund amount before cancelling)
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/refund-preview/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### 16. Cancel My Event Booking (User cancellation)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "{{transactionId}}",
  "reason": "Cannot attend due to personal reasons"
}

#==========================================================
# RECENT BOOKINGS (Organizer Dashboard)
#==========================================================

### 17. Get Recent Event Bookings (Organizer)
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/recent?bookingType=EVENT&limit=10&page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 18. Get Recent Event Bookings — Filter by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/recent?bookingType=EVENT&status=PAID&limit=10&page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 19. Get Recent Event Bookings — Filter by Event
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/recent?eventId={{eventId}}&limit=10&page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}



### 15. Cancel an Event (Organizer/Admin cancels event and processes all refunds)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/cancel-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "6a4c86a07b447e79facca6ce",
  "reason": "Cancelled due to severe weather conditions"
}


#==========================================================
# COURSE ATTENDEE MANAGEMENT (Organizer)
#==========================================================

### 20. Get Course Enrolled Users List
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/course/{{courseId}}/attendees
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 20b. Get Course Enrolled Users — Filtered by Batch
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/course/{{courseId}}/attendees?batchId=6a216d3aaf039f44dc5d6ef9
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 20c. Get Course Enrolled Users — Paginated, Search by Name or bookingId (single field)
GET {{baseUrl}}/booking/course/{{courseId}}/attendees?page=1&limit=5&search=New
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

