# FREE EVENT BOOKING FLOW (Price 0)
#==========================================================

### 21. Calculate Free Event Booking (Preview)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/calculate
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "tickets": [
        {
            "ticketId": "6a353153c1d17af49fd534ee",
            "qty": 1
        },
        {
            "ticketId": "6a353153c1d17af49fd534ed",
            "qty": 1
        }
    ],
    "discountCode": "REF2D7FF8CD",
    "bookingType": "EVENT",
    "eventId": "6a32a0c4e2bd24361039fb72"
}

### 22. Initiate Free Event Booking (Auto-confirms to PAID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/initiate
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "{{eventId}}",
  "tickets": [
    { "ticketId": "{{ticketId}}", "qty": 1 }
  ]
}


### 23. Calculate Ticketless Free Entry Booking (Omit ticket details entirely)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/calculate
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingType": "EVENT",
  "eventId": "6a33ef293858cc62aa600c07"
}


### 24. Direct Enrollment for Ticketless Free Entry Event (Auto-confirms to PAID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/booking/direct-enroll
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingType": "EVENT",
  "eventId": "6a33ef293858cc62aa600c07"
}


